      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i bother getting up anymore. the nerve pain is just constant. it's like my skin is being peeled off 24/7 and there's nothing doctors can do. i'm just so tired of fighting a losing battle. everything feels so heavy and pointless.",
